## ClawAPI Backend
Base: https://clawapi.shareos.ai

### Endpoints

**Master:**
- POST /api/polsia/analyze — {url} → runs full pipeline
- GET /api/polsia/status/{domain} — check analysis progress

**Data:**
- GET /api/polsia/company/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/seo/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/competitors/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/geo/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/social/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/documents/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/email/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/ads/{domain}
- GET /api/polsia/feed/{domain}

**Actions:**
- POST /api/polsia/scrape — {url}
- POST /api/polsia/brand-dna — {url}
- POST /api/polsia/seo/audit — {url}
- POST /api/polsia/competitors/find — {url}
- POST /api/polsia/geo/check — {url}
- POST /api/polsia/patents/search — {query, domain?}
- POST /api/polsia/grants/search — {query, domain?}
- POST /api/polsia/social/post — {domain, platform, content}
- POST /api/polsia/documents/generate — {domain, doc_type}
- POST /api/polsia/email/outreach — {domain, recipients, subject, body}
- POST /api/polsia/ads/create — {domain, platform, headline, description, budget}

**Chat:**
- POST /chat — {message, session_id, stream: true}

## MongoDB Collections
- polsia_okara_companies — scraped company data + brand DNA
- polsia_okara_brand_dna — brand DNA analysis
- polsia_okara_seo — SEO audit results
- polsia_okara_competitors — competitor analysis
- polsia_okara_geo — AI search visibility
- polsia_okara_social — social media posts
- polsia_okara_documents — generated documents
- polsia_okara_email — email campaigns
- polsia_okara_ads — ad campaigns
- polsia_okara_patents — patent searches
- polsia_okara_grants — grant searches
- polsia_okara_feed — activity feed

## Chat Context
When using the dashboard chat, pass context about current company and tab to help OS make relevant changes.
